'''万维网'''（{{Lang-en|World Wide Web}}）亦作'''{{Lang|en|WWW}}'''、'''{{Lang|en|Web}}'''、'''全球广域网'''，是一个透过[[互联网|互联网]]访问的，由许多互相链接的[[超文本|超文本]]组成的[[信息系统|資訊系統]]<ref>{{cite web |title=What is the difference between the Web and the Internet? |url=https://www.w3.org/Help/#webinternet |publisher=World Wide Web Consortium |access-date=2016-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422072749/http://www.w3.org/Help/#webinternet |archive-date=2016-04-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。英國科學家[[蒂姆·伯纳斯-李|蒂姆·伯纳斯-李]]於1989年發明了萬維網。1990年他在瑞士[[CERN|CERN]]的工作期間編寫了第一個[[網頁瀏覽器|網頁瀏覽器]]<ref>{{cite book |first=Stephanie Sammartino |last=McPherson |title=Tim Berners-Lee: Inventor of the World Wide Web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wK0xBWfL9GkC |year=2009 |publisher=Twenty-First Century Books |access-date=2017-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317095420/https://books.google.com/books?id=wK0xBWfL9GkC |archive-date=2017-03-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="AHT">{{cite news
|title = Network Designer Tim Berners-Lee
|url = http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,990627,00.html
|work = Time Magazine
|access-date = 2010-05-17
|quote = He wove the World Wide Web and created a mass medium for the 21st century. The World Wide Web is Berners-Lee's alone. He designed it. He loosed it on the world. And he more than anyone else has fought to keep it open, nonproprietary and free.
